1110:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart.c ****   *         of u16 provided through pData.
1111:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @note When FIFO mode is enabled, writing a data in the TDR register adds one
